snippet.title: Slay the Princess - The Pristine Cut - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011143

Slay the Princess - The Pristine Cut - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games

Slay the Princess - The Pristine Cut is coming to PlayStation this Fall!
You're on a path in the woods, and at the end of that path is a cabin. And in the basement of that cabin is a Princess. You're here to slay her. If you don't, it will be the end of the world.

#ps5 #ps5games
